---

### **Incident Model**

* Title
* Description
* Severity
* Status
* Assigned user
* Pipeline run ID
* Escalation status
* Timestamps

---

### **Escalation Model**

* Incident reference
* Previous assignee
* New assignee
* Reason
* Trigger type (auto/manual)
* Timestamp

